Prerequisites
=============

The SVC library uses the ATerm library (http://www.cwi.nl/projects/MetaEnv/aterm)


Architectures
=============

So far, the SVC library was tested on the following architectures
* sgi   (irix  6.5)
* sparc (sunos 5.6)
*       (linux ???)
